{"tid":126982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本定台灣 旅行達人入","createTime":"2017-02-19T18:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T15:05:43.000Z","uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94f462a28b276678b180026d2c41575aa5fc47b6","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"嚟緊5月完咗DSE想自己一個去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊年12月聖誕去咗台灣 平靚正 <br />\n未去過日本，弊在自己日文唔識多句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔打算瘋狂購物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係想靜靜咁一個人行下睇下景<br />\n兩個地方都想去，budget唔係問題，旨在想散心，呢排開始厭世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對身邊人事都無咩留戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc32b2d9b89347e9667b5b4fa5b4a49a7ae0c997","tid":126982,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24b093bf2e6b7fcfe052ea5a5c0a234834bb1ea","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去台灣有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去六日有四日病到就死<br />\n勝在5月機票夠平，住宿又平，食嘢又平<br />\n好多同學朋友去過日本，餵鹿好似幾正咁好心動，不過未諗好目的地"},{"pid":"3460560e5cca3d36b4ff27f0e61f43f96f380ebd","tid":126982,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"日本一樣可以做到平靚正<br />\n<br />\n有漢字同google translate其實唔成問題"},{"pid":"b2082bf0c3c97df2780c12ec78f5419317841c23","tid":126982,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"日本不解釋"},{"pid":"d8d1374aac3addd869e8e7db2816eb695548e1fa","tid":126982,"uid":70876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e896a85c2381cb06ea43858d808a07bedeee63a0","tid":126982,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去台灣有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去六日有四日病到就死<br />\n勝在5月機票夠平，住宿又平，食嘢又平<br />\n好多同學朋友去過日本，餵鹿好似幾正咁好心動，不過未諗好目的地</blockquote><br />\n日本唔通唔會病咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上次去都病左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本真係好靚我冇否認呀<br />\n<br />\n不過你去完日本會睇台灣唔上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以去左台灣先，一步一步黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重申多次我都係咁<br />\n<br />\n初初打工都係去台灣先。去晒成個台灣喇，跟住越大搵多少少錢，就開始去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016b72ee18c81d10852d0e1ba702f1fa7da202a6","tid":126982,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">旨在想散心，呢排開始厭世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對身邊人事都無咩留戀</span><br />\n<br />\n好建議樓主去四國八十八去遍路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b6bacdc180fd57807ac39daf0b84212e9d8187","tid":126982,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"如果對自己語言溝通把握唔夠 台灣 <br />\n唔係就日本"},{"pid":"cab240ccb39d91007ddb9b98ff9fba76a84565aa","tid":126982,"uid":13471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"日本啦<br />\n早兩個月去完 <br />\n有啲sales 直接拎張中日對照既表叫我指邊一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ee44903964f3a9afb517a48a5060a3fc8f45b","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本一樣可以做到平靚正<br />\n<br />\n有漢字同google translate其實唔成問題</blockquote><br />\n我睇過機票住宿其實唔貴，最擔心係語言不通加上我係路痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017df4f9a9eb5499deee484496ee9738815a4346","tid":126982,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本一樣可以做到平靚正<br />\n<br />\n有漢字同google translate其實唔成問題</blockquote><br />\n我睇過機票住宿其實唔貴，最擔心係語言不通加上我係路痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔洗驚 大把人都識普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多咪用google translate<br />\n我去果時都係用國際語言 thisthisthis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5439518d48b22c7a681a45b78a2e0a45a3ecda65","tid":126982,"uid":45016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"日本去遊客區好多識講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去過日本之後<br />\n台灣韓國 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5625f303b8f388d5f30f9ee7a5b0e15e711e9bc","tid":126982,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"日本 for sure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d82df8e3291bfd89a8f8f8b4258f7a13c7345c6","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去台灣有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去六日有四日病到就死<br />\n勝在5月機票夠平，住宿又平，食嘢又平<br />\n好多同學朋友去過日本，餵鹿好似幾正咁好心動，不過未諗好目的地</blockquote><br />\n日本唔通唔會病咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上次去都病左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本真係好靚我冇否認呀<br />\n<br />\n不過你去完日本會睇台灣唔上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以去左台灣先，一步一步黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重申多次我都係咁<br />\n<br />\n初初打工都係去台灣先。去晒成個台灣喇，跟住越大搵多少少錢，就開始去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想離開下身邊環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好辛苦<br />\n只要有得靜下唔使煩咁多嘢就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊年去咗台灣，係好平好平<br />\n所以計劃下去日本"},{"pid":"df8bad4e34f43eda978b90f74a1325b54160a3f9","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">旨在想散心，呢排開始厭世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對身邊人事都無咩留戀</span><br />\n<br />\n好建議樓主去四國八十八去遍路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能未行完已經死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f57fdeb736bd14a4fd530ccf2f9735bb486188","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本去遊客區好多識講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去過日本之後<br />\n台灣韓國 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣勝在好平 機票住宿食飯最抵3000有找"},{"pid":"cc93ce0d15605fdea5d208000f8b3de14a38fc48","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本啦<br />\n早兩個月去完 <br />\n有啲sales 直接拎張中日對照既表叫我指邊一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你去咗邊個地區？"},{"pid":"3d312257f75201e0b490171c5f7d2110bce77137","tid":126982,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本一樣可以做到平靚正<br />\n<br />\n有漢字同google translate其實唔成問題</blockquote><br />\n我睇過機票住宿其實唔貴，最擔心係語言不通加上我係路痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔洗驚 大把人都識普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多咪用google translate<br />\n我去果時都係用國際語言 thisthisthis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講我啲同學去日本用英文問路，個日本仔即刻掉頭走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73489368ca1a7af9dec719e5d6be85e7b32db931","tid":126982,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議去晒台灣先好踏足日本<br />\n<br />\n因為你遊過日本就唔想去其他地方<br />\n<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去台灣有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去六日有四日病到就死<br />\n勝在5月機票夠平，住宿又平，食嘢又平<br />\n好多同學朋友去過日本，餵鹿好似幾正咁好心動，不過未諗好目的地</blockquote><br />\n你已經有answer, 仲上嚟問乜？"},{"pid":"37534a7a28b6b542ba7ed8aa42bb00ee5f14670f","tid":126982,"uid":80305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"睇境 京都好靚好多野睇<br />\n台灣既靚境無咁多<br />\n睇筆直啦"}]}